      <title>泰国反对派攻击总理经济失败，Thaksin Clout</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/thai-opposition-assails-pm-for-economic-failures-thaksin-clout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国的主要反对党指责总理佩顿顿·辛纳瓦特拉（Paetongtarn Shinawatra）允许她的父亲塔克辛·辛瓦瓦特拉（Thaksin Shinawatra）不适当地影响了政府的政策，并且未能解决关键的经济问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/thai-opposition-assails-pm-for-economic-failures-thaksin-clout</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 06:14:25 GMT</pubDate>
